parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the lack of proper protection in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light on the dashboard flashes or remains on
airbag deploys unnecessarily
airbag fails to deploy in a crash
smoke or burn holes in the airbag
false readings from the sensor unit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning yaw rate sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to unnecessary deployments or failures to deploy, which can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Yaw rate sensor malfunctioning
airbag warning light on the dashboard flashes or remains on
airbag deploys unnecessarily
airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Brakes lock up
vehicle fails to slow down or stop
no tire marks or skid marks on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to accidents or injuries, as the airbag may not deploy properly in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light comes on
flashes
or stays on; seatbelts do not lock in place during sudden stops; seatbelt retractors do not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ECM can cause the vehicle to stall or become difficult to start, leading to potential accidents or strandings.
symptoms: Vehicle slowly loses power
difficulty starting the engine
strange behavior when trying to start the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause fires, smoke, or electrical malfunctions, leading to potential accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Smoke coming from the dashboard
electrical burning smell
fuses blowing
interior lights and accessories malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery terminal can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to potential accidents or strandings.
symptoms: Positive terminal coming loose
loss of power while driving
risk of accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the multi-sensing system can lead to accidents or injuries, as the system may not detect obstacles or provide proper warnings.
symptoms: Failure to detect obstacles
lack of warning beeps or signals
rear camera malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shifter assembly can cause the vehicle to become stuck in a particular gear, making it difficult or impossible to drive, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifter gets stuck
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the vehicle is stuck in a particular gear
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective transmission cooler can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to difficulties shifting gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission cooler is defective
the transmission is unable to shift into gear
the transmission hesitates or jerks when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature clutch failure can cause the vehicle to become difficult or impossible to drive, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.
